com.b2international.snowowl.snomed.snomedrefset

Interface SnomedConcreteDataTypeRefSetMember

  • All Superinterfaces:
    org.eclipse.emf.cdo.CDOObject, org.eclipse.emf.cdo.common.id.CDOWithID, org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier, SnomedRefSetMember
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    Rf2RefSetMember, SnomedConcreteDataTypeRefSetMemberImpl, UnsupportedRf2RefSetMember

    public interface SnomedConcreteDataTypeRefSetMember
extends SnomedRefSetMember
    Representation of a SNOMED CT data type reference set member.

    The following features are supported:

    • Serialized Value
    • Label
    • Uom Component Id
    • Operator Component Id
    • Data Type
    • Characteristic Type Id

    See Also:
    SnomedRefSetPackage.getSnomedConcreteDataTypeRefSetMember()
